29 (B) acted in concert with another person who requested
30 emergency medical assistance;
31 for an individual who reasonably appeared to be in need of
32 medical assistance due to the use of alcohol or a controlled
33 substance.
34 (13) The person has posttraumatic stress disorder, traumatic brain
