36 (14) The person is a person described in IC 31-30-1-4(d) who
37 committed the offense while the person was a child but is now at
38 least twenty-one (21) years of age.
39 (15) The offense involved a controlled substance under
40 IC 35-48-4 and the person:
41 (A) sought treatment:
42 (i) in the three hundred sixty-five (365) day period
